{"tid":2362414,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"【詳細教學】有冇連登作者願意一齊轉場去Mewe開page/group呀？","createTime":"2021-01-11T12:10:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T10:06:59.000Z","uid":218219,"like":32,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"01efcb8427a025a9ecb77190a7a4799e814acda3","tid":2362414,"uid":218219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:10:09.000Z","msg":"大家好我係小野菊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />平時得閒會係度寫下故嘅人<br />\n以我所知唔少連登作者都有用fb同ig開page嘅<br />\n今日想係度宣傳下Mewe呢個新平台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n畀錢同唔畀錢都任君選擇，希望吸引到大家轉場啦<br />\n<br />\n以我所知Mewe開page要月費15蚊<br />\n其實都唔算好貴嘅，fans多嘅作者值得開嚟用，當係支持平台<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/66FSWma.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F66FSWma.jpg&h=75917bfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">唔好失望走住！<br />\n仲有一個方法！</span></span></strong><br />\n你都可以選擇開group，只要轉一轉啲setting其實同用page嘅功能都差不多<br />\n（e.g. 讀者唔可以出post，但可以留言同Invite其他人）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>首先<strong><span class=\"red\">身為作者</span></strong>嘅你<br />\n要先開一個分身戶口，免得真名上Mewe啦</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ZVjBtp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ZVjBtp.jpg&h=521dee7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後去Communities度開一個新Group<br />\n「Start a new group」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SUiUqmZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSUiUqmZ.jpg&h=d6229e58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R8Nqw1H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR8Nqw1H.jpg&h=fff8ff5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而<strong><span class=\"red\"><ins>身為讀者</ins></span></strong>嘅你，點樣搵你心愛嘅作者呢？<br />\n搵Group可以去Communities呢度搵<br />\n例子如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DUOxbYR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDUOxbYR.jpg&h=03f804bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n作者係唔會見到讀者私人account入面嘅Private Post嘅，<br />\n大家可以放心！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><ins>各位作者開Group轉Setting教學：</ins></span></strong><br />\n轉讀者嘅permission，等讀者冇得出post，<br />\n但讀者照樣可以留言、入Group Chat吹水<br />\n以及invite其他人去入group<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mCn9YBr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmCn9YBr.jpg&h=a78a6cae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4PcqwWp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4PcqwWp.jpg&h=20d85803&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s9SxWn3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs9SxWn3.jpg&h=88736d52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ui3M0PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUi3M0PH.jpg&h=e1c26b94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3BCn21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3BCn21.jpg&h=f20f0d88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此外，記得set你個group做公開，咁就人人都可以支持你喇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AJr3iDm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAJr3iDm.jpg&h=9241af7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YPnU9K0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYPnU9K0.jpg&h=500f1e51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ziHaH4Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FziHaH4Z.jpg&h=79e3bcc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後講咗咁耐，就係自我宣傳時間啦<br />\n歡迎各位作者讀者一齊轉場加我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">啊&hellip;&hellip;咪住！</span></strong><br />\n教埋大家點樣搵條Link出嚟Share畀讀者Add你先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TkFGPNV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTkFGPNV.jpg&h=9e032f43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XNMVUey.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXNMVUey.jpg&h=c2965e4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QT4o3aE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQT4o3aE.jpg&h=5b2bcc04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就會整到一條咁嘅Link出嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://mewe.com/join/小野菊\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fjoin%2F%E5%B0%8F%E9%87%8E%E8%8F%8A&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BfGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=45e05a40\" target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/join/小野菊</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實我都係Mewe新用戶<br />\n好多嘢都未學識整<br />\n希望大家手下留情，多多指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73162301a91272c8bbe765843e77e8ad7287223d","tid":2362414,"uid":55658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:11:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bcf6fe0ff039ff589353a75d2c5d54e110ae6198","tid":2362414,"uid":218219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73162301a91272c8bbe765843e77e8ad7287223d","tid":2362414,"uid":55658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:11:28.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:12:01.000Z","msg":"謝謝你"},{"pid":"0318ca7d865c216582df3027a266744d5e168092","tid":2362414,"uid":323360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:12:16.000Z","msg":"十卜"},{"pid":"076d41069a241f123f830d87a1832ab5b0228ee7","tid":2362414,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:12:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c40ffd82198127b91cd2156b08a056ea4b9ccd4","tid":2362414,"uid":218219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"076d41069a241f123f830d87a1832ab5b0228ee7","tid":2362414,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:12:30.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:14: